column5: Hi guys, I have 2 one man chair pop over huts and I would like to get the 2 man version. dose anyone know where I can get one? Any one selling one?  I have the pex1 and would like the pex2  http://www.icefish.com/catalog/inventory.php?fam=127&cat=104  Thanks Alex,
Le Baron had them last year.  Not sure about this year.
